sentences.english: Okay , now the Mastodon is from the semi - late Jurassic period.

sentences.english: The man in this picture is holding a mastodon tooth that was found not very long ago.

sentences.english: She is losing her baby teeth and getting permanent teeth.

sentences.english: One of the animals whose bones archeologists study is the mastodon.
sentences.chinese: 他們研究的動物骨骸之一，就是乳齒象。
